1. *Pokušali* smo da izdržimo sve izazove (We tried to endure all challenges).
2. Oni su se *pokušali* da odbrane od napada (They tried to defend themselves from attack).
3. *Pokušavali* su da izgrade novi život (They were trying to build a new life).
4. Mi smo se *pokušavali* da učinimo svoje najbolje (We were trying to do our best).
5. Oni su *pokušali* da nas ubede da je to dobra ideja (They tried to convince us that it was a good idea).
6. *Pokušao* je da se izbori za svoje pravo (He tried to fight for his right).